business_definition: Main group containing date and time information in various formats for system processing and display purposes
Group containing current date and time data in numeric format
Group containing current date components in YYYYMMDD format
Four-digit year component of the current date
Two-digit month component of the current date (01-12)
Two-digit day component of the current date (01-31)
Numeric representation of current date in YYYYMMDD format (REDEFINES WS-CURDATE)
Group containing current time components in HHMMSSCC format
Two-digit hours component of the current time (00-23)
Two-digit minutes component of the current time (00-59)
Two-digit seconds component of the current time (00-59)
Two-digit centiseconds component of the current time (00-99)
Numeric representation of current time in HHMMSSCC format (REDEFINES WS-CURTIME)
Group containing current date formatted as MM/DD/YY for display purposes
Two-digit month component for MM/DD/YY format
